# Usage

Provides endpoints for viewing a list of usage for all your Containers and [Servers](#hosts). <%= application_name %> keeps track of resource usage as the time periods  that a resource was in use. A new usage record is created every time a resource is started or stopped. Each usage record includes the applied pricing and accumulated charges during the interval. Price is based on the assigned [service plan](#service-plans).

This endpoint outputs usage data in the same format as the [Billing](#billing) api.

## List Usages

```shell
curl "<%= shell_url %>/api/usage"
  -H "Authorization: BEARER <%= shell_token %>"
```

